WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.260 --> 00:00:05.210
Progressive web apps should start
fast and be usable immediately.

00:00:05.210 --> 00:00:09.640
So far, your weather app starts quickly,
but it's not usable.

00:00:09.640 --> 00:00:11.020
There's no data there.

00:00:11.020 --> 00:00:13.760
To be useful, it needs data.

00:00:13.760 --> 00:00:16.930
Let's take a look at how
we can get the data we need

00:00:16.930 --> 00:00:19.470
on the user's first visit to our app.

00:00:19.470 --> 00:00:22.670
Then, render it on screen
as quickly as possible.

